## Scope

This repository contains documentation, methodologies, prompts, protocols and reference material intended to support the use of Large Language Models (LLMs) as investment committees for educational and research purposes.

It is **not** investment advice, financial consulting or a recommendation to buy or sell any asset.

Users remain solely responsible for their investment decisions.

